release_note: Major Release: Delete Account: Now the user can delete their account forever Animated Themes: Introducing animated themes to the app. HashTags: Now the user can add hash tags to their diary entries. Scribble support: Now iPad users can use the Scribble feature while writing a diary with some useful keyboard shortcuts.
A complete design revamp with all new features! Introducing new colour and background themes. Introducing new daily tracker for your weekly progress with graphical user interface.
Added more app themes and backgrounds!
Introducing Themes and Wallpaper Backgrounds : Now user can customise their diary with wide collection of themes and backgrounds!
Users now have the option to remove all ads from the app and unlock many advanced features with just one in app purchase!
